File: sun.cf.howto
	Converting Standard Sun Config Files to Sendmail Version 8
	by Rick McCarty Texas Instruments Inc.
	Document details the changes necessary to continue using 
	your current SunOS sendmail.cf with sendmail version 8.

File: client.cf
	A client.cf file similar to the one developed in
	the tutorial of the book.

File: hostnames.c
	Compile and run this to see how your host's libraries
	determine your machine's canonical name.

File: massagelog.sh
	A simple shell script to sum all mail traffic from
	the syslog file.
